{"version":1,"entries":{"person_19197_translations":{"at":1774211287766,"data":{"id":19197,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"​From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.  \n\nJohn Robinson (born October 25, 1985) is an American actor. He portrayed John McFarland in Gus Van Sant's Elephant and Stacy Peralta in the skateboarding film Lords of Dogtown.\n\nRobinson enjoys snowboarding and played lacrosse in high school. He has also done some modeling. He is a 2005 graduate of the Oregon Episcopal School.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article John Robinson, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"John Robinson","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"约翰·罗宾逊（John Robinson，1985年10月25日-），美国演员。他在格斯·范·桑特的《大象》中饰演约翰·麦克法兰，在滑板电影《狗镇领主》中饰演史黛西·佩拉尔塔。","name":"约翰·罗宾逊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"約翰·羅賓遜（John Robinson，1985 年 10 月 25 日-），美國演員。他在格斯·範·桑特的《永珍之家》中飾演約翰·麥克法蘭，在滑板電影《狗鎮領主》中飾演史黛西·佩拉爾塔。","name":"約翰·羅賓遜","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джон Робинсон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジョン・ロビンソン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джон Робінсон","primary":false}}]}},"person_2548853_translations":{"at":1774211290123,"data":{"id":2548853,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Indy Urban","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Инди Урбан","primary":false}}]}},"tv_300054_keywords":{"at":1774211291266,"data":{"id":300054,"results":[{"name":"martial arts","id":779},{"name":"based on manga","id":13141},{"name":"anime","id":210024},{"name":"original net animation (ona)","id":323096}]}},"person_1318187_translations":{"at":1774211298074,"data":{"id":1318187,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Rebecca Chan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"出生于香港，籍贯广东潮阳，现为无綫电视部头合约女艺员，曾参加1979年度香港小姐竞选。80年代中期更作为女一号主演两部广受欢迎的大型金庸古龙剧：《笑傲江湖》和《陆小凤之凤舞九天》。《笑傲江湖》中陈秀珠饰演任盈盈与周润发合作。后来又因翁美玲的去世，代替她出演《陆小凤之凤舞九天》，与万梓良合作。80年代的陈秀珠可谓是红了又红。 后来的剧集还有《大运河》、《黄大仙》、《大班密令》、《季节》、《誓不低头》、《狂龙》、《亚二一族》等。还饰演过90年内地电视剧《封神榜》中的女娲 。是极受欢迎的TVB当家花旦之一。","name":"陈秀珠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ребекка Чан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陳秀珠，生於香港，籍貫廣東潮陽。她在 1979 年參選香港小姐，雖三甲不入，很快在娛樂圈走紅，與 TVB 簽約。她在 1980 年代中期曾以女主角身份主演兩部廣受歡迎的大型金庸、古龍武俠劇：《笑傲江湖》和《陸小鳳之鳳舞九天》。2000 年代，陳秀珠繼續拍攝了不少無綫電視劇。她曾多次被提名《萬千星輝頒獎典禮》最佳女配角。陳秀珠近年為照顧兒子而減產，但仍以以一年一劇的形式於幕前演出。於 2020 年 7 月離開無綫。","name":"陳秀珠","primary":true}}]}},"person_1674731_translations":{"at":1774211313587,"data":{"id":1674731,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jack Hickey is an award winning Irish television and film actor and director. Jack graduated from the Gaiety School of Acting in 2010\n\nIn 2017, he joined the cast of Emmerdale, as Matt, the father of Carly's (Gemma Atkinson) child. As an actor, Hickey also made appearances in Game Of Thrones, Penny Dreadful and Jericho. He also appeared in the feature films Mary Shelley and Sea Fever alongside Hermione Corfield. His directorial debut film Cynthia won awards at the Galway Film Fleadh and the Irish Film Festival in London. It was also long-listed for the 92nd Academy Awards. The film was made by his production company Cooper Alley Productions he runs with his sister Lara Hickey.\n\nIn 2022, he joined the cast of Netflix series Vikings: Valhalla as Richard II, Duke of Normandy.\n\nHe had a role in the 2024 police procedural drama Borderline. In August 2024, he joined the cast of the sports film Saipan as Niall Quinn, appearing alongside Steve Coogan.","name":"Jack Hickey","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_1625115_translations":{"at":1774211321076,"data":{"id":1625115,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"何昊阳，中央电视台联合日本TBS电视台《华流游美》娱乐节目主持人，音乐录影带，内地歌手罗中旭歌曲《你醒来我醒来》MTV女主角。多家时尚杂志社封面模特，演出过众多影视作品。","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"He Haoyang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"He Haoyang","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"何昊陽，中央電視台聯合日本 TBS 電視台《華流遊美》娛樂節目主持人，音樂錄影帶，內地歌手羅中旭歌曲《你醒來我醒來》MTV 女主角。多家時尚雜誌社封面模特，演出過眾多影視作品。","name":"何昊陽","primary":false}}]}},"person_1689302_translations":{"at":1774211322500,"data":{"id":1689302,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hus Miller","primary":true}}]}},"person_27514_translations":{"at":1774211324002,"data":{"id":27514,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Shecky Greene (born Fred Sheldon Greenfie